    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245970/extras/6341630a78f9d7d060a93f132f1bfd5d.poster.avif?t=1770111421\" width=600 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245970/extras/6341630a78f9d7d060a93f132f1bfd5d.webm?t=1770111421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245970/extras/6341630a78f9d7d060a93f132f1bfd5d.mp4?t=1770111421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全动画、全语音的轻小说游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以东京为舞台，孤独的仿生少女琳邂逅葵，在友情中逐渐找回人性。然而，当琳揭开自己的身世之谜时，故事迎来了重大转折。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245970/extras/197ea6ac7d3c941963ee7fa1be54ec29.avif?t=1770111421\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245970/extras_big/197ea6ac7d3c941963ee7fa1be54ec29.avif?t=1770111421 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  故事大纲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >东京女孩纪事》讲述了两个女孩在东京相遇并建立友谊的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在东京的冷雨中，机器人女孩琳恩独自在公园里感到孤独。 没有感情和记忆的琳渴望与人交流。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑发女孩葵出现了，她轻轻地呼唤琳恩，邀请她到自己的伞下。 渐渐地，两人建立了联系，葵接受了琳是机器人的事实，并理解了她的孤独。 最后，雨停了，彩虹出现了，琳第一次感受到了情感，她觉得与葵的相遇是新生活的开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过与葵的相遇，琳逐渐从友谊中找回了人性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，当琳恩发现自己出生的秘密时，故事出现了重大转折。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245970/extras/86b0d974942ec143679d30c4e5c1fe5b.avif?t=1770111421\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245970/extras_big/86b0d974942ec143679d30c4e5c1fe5b.avif?t=1770111421 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[创作理由］</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >到目前为止，我对轻小说游戏还不是很感兴趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原因是我不喜欢那种类似于故事板的形式，即文字和静态图像。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那么，如果我制作一款轻小说游戏会怎样呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果是全动画的，我可能会感兴趣。 我想，如果我能自己制作，一定会很有趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我希望故事简单，讲述两个女孩之间的羁绊。我选择东京作为背景，是因为我曾经住在东京，对这座城市充满了向往。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245970/extras/449622ba628734596b967d775b33262c.avif?t=1770111421\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245970/extras_big/449622ba628734596b967d775b33262c.avif?t=1770111421 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[探索元素</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在故事的中间，葵还可以通过探索游戏来寻找凛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，玩家必须根据视频中的提示找到凛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245970/extras/f54b9792e604f384ec79e21da6e3785a.avif?t=1770111421\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245970/extras_big/f54b9792e604f384ec79e21da6e3785a.avif?t=1770111421 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[如何开始游戏］</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首先，按下开场按钮并欣赏开场电影。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看完电影后，按下按钮返回标题屏幕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这时会出现下一章按钮，您可以从这里开始继续故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245970/extras/ea20761aba2b8473d56319128825cfca.avif?t=1770111421\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245970/extras_big/ea20761aba2b8473d56319128825cfca.avif?t=1770111421 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏发行信息  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >允许分发本游戏至 “艾米丽的故事”。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为防止剧透，禁止传播之后的故事。</p>",
